| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4095 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: fd443e6f-7b54-5ef5-ac26-6f1fea992b2e"
